Add a Webex App widget
You can add Webex App widgets to the home screen of your iPhone, iPad, or Android, as a quick way to access meeting, messaging, and calling information without having to open the app.
iOS
Android
1
From the home screen, touch and hold until the apps jiggle.
2
Tap add + in the top upper-left corner.
3
Search for Webex, tap to add, and swipe to choose which widget you want to have on the home screen.
Recent Directs
Upcoming Meetings
Call settings
4
Tap Add widget.